{"tid":1303183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國抵制寶礦力？等我唸下點講先！","createTime":"2019-07-10T08:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T12:14:00.000Z","uid":187972,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5095d073cbe692dcbf4d789f2e82885215cb408a","tid":1303183,"uid":187972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:21:05.000Z","msg":"我覺得官方可以從以下角度回應<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以下純自膠非官方回應</span></span><br />\n本人扮官腔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">鑒於近期中國內地朋友對於我公司撤TVB廣告一事的激烈反應，我公司有以下幾點回應.<br />\n 1.本公司撤出TVB廣告與港獨無關，鑒於TVB公信力大幅下降影響本產品給予大眾的正面印象，所以決定撤出TVB.<br />\n2.本公司撤出TVB廣告於TVB播放內容無關，其他媒體頻道亦有播放內地傳言相關攻擊警察片段，甚至比TVB更加完整，所以重申和任何片段無關.<br />\n3.TVB影響本公司廣告受眾，將成為無效廣告，所以決定撤出TVB的廣告.本公司商品面向的年齡層是青少年，以及運動人士，其中青少年是本公司最重要的推廣層面，而TVB近期的公信力下降所導致大量青少年觀眾流失，導致我公司廣告很可能成為無效廣告，所以從商業層面，我公司最終決定撤出TVB廣告. </span><br />\n<br />\n中意俾正評，唔中意就負皮，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以上純屬個人自膠，與寶礦力官方無關.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d51034085ad0643504dadea33943f592697266c","tid":1303183,"uid":187972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:23:27.000Z","msg":"自推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"b9771091df354ea47c899fc27821dc6ecd552167","tid":1303183,"uid":376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:26:29.000Z","msg":"大陸本身就冇咩人飲寶礦力"},{"pid":"642de3a95df5b77344512ee87a232e45cfadb6b8","tid":1303183,"uid":187972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,